source.name: ENERGY STAR Find A Product
source.description: Tool to search for ENERGY STAR qualified products based on specific attributes.  Currently there is a Find A Product query for Computers, Imaging Equipment, Monitors, Televisions, Home Audio, DVD Players, Combination Units and Telephony. ENERGY STAR is a joint program of the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency and the U.S. Department of Energy helping us all save money and protect the environment through energy efficient products and practices.
